  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power\ncompany will pay for the reinforc-\nIng of the North Howard street\nbridge which Commissioner ONO\nclosed yesterday to traffic. Mr..\nONO met officials of the company\nthis morning and they agreed that\nthe city should go ahead with the\nwork and the Washington Water\nPower company should pay the ex-\npense.\n\n\nMen will be started to work In\nthe morning and the work will be\ncompleted in 10 days."
    }
